AnyEvent-Sphinx version 0.01
============================

AnyEvent based aync inerface to the Sphinx search engine.  This code
heavily borrows from the Sphinx::Search module found on CPAN.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  blah blah blah

